  "elapsed_s": 113.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The thing what was the most important in these competitions for me that I realize later on was actually not the prize that I took.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I took the special prize and the golden medal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But one little package that I receive as a present of a [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] anonymous donor, donor that didn't left-- he's anonymous.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Left his name, and his address, and his phone number.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Did not.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Did not.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was very little package.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Perhaps didn't left it because of fears that will be traced after that by the police, local police.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was in Romania.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Romania.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now we're speaking about the '60s was one difficult period of their political life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I received, received this package, but I didn't open, even.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I opened after I left the airport in Italy, was where I returned from Romania.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And what was my surprise when I saw this very little letter, this from friend.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I hope that this music will enhance your repertoire later on in your life with my best wishes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is music of Jewish composers that disappear during the Second World War.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [SIGHS] Of course, this was when this idea for starting this collection that later on I called Lost Voices started.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] There were pieces of absolutely unknown composers to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But nevertheless, when I started to dig inside of the music, I very soon saw that this is one very special music and even more dear to me, not only because was written by people that died because they were Jewish-- we would like to say, maybe, martyrs of the Jewish culture-- but because of the value of the music that I succeed.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I hope that to obtain.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
